'''[[服装|服装]]'''是[[人类形象|人类形象]]基础的一部分，除了满足基本的保护和修饰功能之外，它的每个配件也传达出不同的[[文化|文化]]和[[社会|社会]]意义，在绝大多数的人文社会中都有属于自己的'''着装守则'''，其中的大部分规则都是[[不成文规定|不成文规定]]但被大多数人所接受的。而着装守则的主要目的通常是为了传达着装者的某种讯息，例如着装者的[[职业|职业]]、社会地位、[[社會性別|社會性別]]、[[宗教|宗教]]信仰、[[性暗示|性暗示]]及其他。

有一些地方的學校，例如[[亞洲|亞洲]]的一些國家，都要求學生穿著[[校服|校服]]上學，<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20160819/37352811/|title=管了百年 高中制服解禁|last=|first=|date=|work=|newspaper=蘋果日報|accessdate=2017-03-03|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2017-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170917231748/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20160819/37352811/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://opinion.udn.com/opinion/story/6072/1757963|title=廢除服儀規定，才是制服文化的開始？|accessdate=2017-03-03|author=劉揚銘|date=|work=鳴人堂|publisher=|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920212327/https://opinion.udn.com/opinion/story/6072/1757963|dead-url=no}}</ref>一些地方甚至對學生的髮型有所規範，而對髮型的規範又稱為「[[髮禁|髮禁]]」。很多其他的職業，如軍隊、警察、僧侶、神職人員等，也有自己的制服和髮型規定；很多私人企業也會對員工的服裝儀容甚至髮型做出規範，一些社交場合也會對參與者服裝儀容和髮型等做出規範。

要求服裝儀容規範可能有好處，像例如就學校的情境而言，盡管有些研究認為制服無助改善學生的課業和行為表現<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Ryan Yeung |title=Are School Uniforms a Good Fit?: Results From the ECLS-K and the NELS |date=2009-10-22 |doi=10.1177/0895904808330170 |url=https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/abs/10.1177/0895904808330170 |journal= |access-date=2021-02-15 |archive-date=2020-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114003323/https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/abs/10.1177/0895904808330170 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=David L. Brunsma &Kerry A. Rockquemore |title=Effects of Student Uniforms on Attendance, Behavior Problems, Substance Use, and Academic Achievement |journal=The Journal of Educational Research |date=1998 |volume=92 |issue=1 |pages=53-62 |doi=10.1080/00220679809597575 |url=https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/00220679809597575 |access-date=2021-02-15 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127015500/https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/00220679809597575 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但也有相當數量的研究顯示，引進學校制服有助改善學生整體的課業和行為表現。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Chris Baumann , Hana Krskova |title=School discipline, school uniforms and academic performance |journal=International Journal of Educational Management |date=2016-08-08 |volume=30 |issue=6 |pages=1003-1029 |doi=10.1108/IJEM-09-2015-0118 |url=https://www.emerald.com/insight/content/doi/10.1108/IJEM-09-2015-0118/full/html |accessdate=2021-02-15 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127130535/https://www.emerald.com/insight/content/doi/10.1108/IJEM-09-2015-0118/full/html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=Elisabetta Gentile, Scott A. Imberman |title=Dressed for success? The effect of school uniforms on student achievement and behavior |journal=Journal of Urban Economics |date=2012-01 |volume=71 |issue=1 |pages=1-17 |doi=10.1016/j.jue.2011.10.002 |url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0094119011000611 |accessdate=2021-02-15 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127221924/https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0094119011000611 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=Ann Bodine |title=School Uniforms, Academic Achievement, and Uses of Research |journal=The Journal of Educational Research |date=2003 |volume=97 |issue=2 |pages=67-71 |doi=10.1080/00220670309597509 |url=https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/00220670309597509 |access-date=2021-02-15 |archive-date=2021-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211221094932/https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/00220670309597509 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；比起沒有制服的學校，有制服的學校的老師所感受的校園幫派活動校少，反之比起有制服的學校，沒有制服的學校的學生有較高的自我知覺。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Kathleen Kiley Wade, Mary E. Stafford |title=Public School Uniforms: Effect on Perceptions of Gang Presence, School Climate, and Student Self-Perceptions |journal=Education and Urban Society |date=2003-08-01 |volume=35 |issue=4 |pages=399-420 |doi=10.1177/0013124503255002 |url=https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/abs/10.1177/0013124503255002 |access-date=2021-02-15 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109031456/https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/abs/10.1177/0013124503255002 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Denise-Marie Ordway |title=School uniforms: Do they really improve student achievement, behavior? |url=https://journalistsresource.org/studies/society/education/school-uniforms-research-achievement/ |website=Journalist's Resource |accessdate=2021-02-15 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203024742/http://journalistsresource.org/studies/society/education/school-uniforms-research-achievement/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

